### Feedback System API Test Suite
### Covers: Public GET, Public POST, Admin Config + Validation

### ACTIVE feedback (should load form)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-valid-003

### EXPIRED feedback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-expired-001

### ALREADY RESPONDED feedback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-used-001

### INVALID feedback ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/not-found

### VALID submission (use a fresh ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-valid-004/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5
}

### INVALID rating (out of range)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-valid-005/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 10
}

### EXPIRED feedback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-expired-001/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4
}

### ALREADY USED feedback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/fb-used-001/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 3
}

### INVALID feedback ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/public/feedback/not-found/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 2
}

### VALID admin config update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "Rate your chatbot experience",
  "headerDescription": "Tell us how helpful the chatbot was.",
  "footerText": "We value your feedback.",
  "ratingLabels": ["Terrible", "Bad", "Neutral", "Good", "Excellent"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks for your feedback!",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid feedback link.",
  "expiredReplyText": "This link has expired.",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM"]
}

### INVALID - header is blank
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "",
  "headerDescription": "Test",
  "footerText": "Test",
  "ratingLabels": ["Bad", "Okay", "Good", "Very Good", "Excellent"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid",
  "expiredReplyText": "Expired",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM"]
}

### INVALID - rating labels not equal to 5
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "Test Header",
  "headerDescription": "Test",
  "footerText": "Test",
  "ratingLabels": ["Bad", "Okay", "Good"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid",
  "expiredReplyText": "Expired",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM"]
}

### INVALID - rating label blank
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "Test Header",
  "headerDescription": "Test",
  "footerText": "Test",
  "ratingLabels": ["Bad", "", "Good", "Very Good", "Excellent"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid",
  "expiredReplyText": "Expired",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM"]
}

### INVALID - duplicate skip channels
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "Test Header",
  "headerDescription": "Test",
  "footerText": "Test",
  "ratingLabels": ["Bad", "Okay", "Good", "Very Good", "Excellent"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid",
  "expiredReplyText": "Expired",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM", "INSTAGRAM"]
}

### INVALID - header too long
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/enterprises/acme-bank/session-feedback-form
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enterpriseId": "acme-bank",
  "headerText": "This header text is intentionally written to exceed the maximum allowed character limit set in the validation logic for testing purposes.",
  "headerDescription": "Test",
  "footerText": "Test",
  "ratingLabels": ["Bad", "Okay", "Good", "Very Good", "Excellent"],
  "thankYouText": "Thanks",
  "invalidReplyText": "Invalid",
  "expiredReplyText": "Expired",
  "skipForChannels": ["INSTAGRAM"]
}



